          <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">198</NUMEX> (<NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">18.4%</NUMEX>) of the controls (<ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">P < 0.001</ENAMEX>) met the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">ATP</ENAMEX>
          III criteria. The <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">metabolic syndrome</ENAMEX> was more frequent in
