          <NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">33%</NUMEX>, p = <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">0.420</NUMEX>). About the <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">one half</NUMEX> of the controls and
          <NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">60%</NUMEX> of the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">patients</ENAMEX> with the <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">metabolic syndrome</ENAMEX> reported
