        produce (including antithrombotic and anti-inflammatory
        effects) [ <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">22 23</NUMEX> ] . In accordance to that, several
        <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">investigators</ENAMEX> have reported that non-pharmacological
